OL,3,COldham Council to demand public
OL,4,Cinquiry into child sexual exploitation
OL,6,FOldham Council will demand a statutory
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry into historic and
OL,8,Fcurrent child sexual exploitation
OL,9,Ffollowing an extraordinary meeting of
OL,10,Fthe authority.
OL,12,FLast night's session was called by
OL,13,FOldham's Conservative Group and the
OL,14,Fmotion was passed unanimously by
OL,15,Fmembers.
