OL,3,COldham Council to demand public
OL,4,Cinquiry into child sexual exploitation
OL,6,FA judge-backed review would give the
OL,7,Fcouncil more power to demand evidence
OL,8,Ffrom governmental institutions than
OL,9,Fwhat has been described as a 'Telford-
OL,10,Fstyle' local inquiry currently planned
OL,11,Ffor the borough.
OL,13,FThe decision comes just three months
OL,14,Fafter a previous request for a
OL,15,Fgovernment-led review was rejected by
OL,16,Fthe home secretary, sparking a major
OL,17,Fpublic backlash.
