OL,3,COldham Council to demand public
OL,4,Cinquiry into child sexual exploitation
OL,6,FCouncillor Lewis Quigg, who proposed
OL,7,Fthe motion, said: "This national
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry is to right an
OL,9,Fincredible wrong. It's about time that
OL,10,Fthe lid is lifted on this disaster,
OL,11,Fthis national scandal of children who
OL,12,Fhave been abused in some of the most
OL,13,Fevil acts."
OL,15,FCouncillor David Arnott added the
OL,16,Fissue had 'hung over this borough for
OL,17,Ffar too long' and that the council had
OL,18,F'failed many times to stop horrific
OL,19,Fabuses continuing for years'.
