OL,4,Cinquiry into child sexual exploitation
OL,6,FThe motion includes changes in
OL,7,Flanguage to avoid inflicting further
OL,8,Ftrauma on survivors and victims of
OL,9,Fchild sexual exploitation, a
OL,10,Fcommitment to putting victims' voices
OL,11,Fat the centre of any new inquiry and
OL,12,Fcalling upon the Greater Manchester
OL,13,FCombined Authority to lend their voice
OL,14,Fto the call for statutory powers.
